      "text": "2. Throttle body inspection"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "With the steering wheel in the straight ahead position, check the relative throttle opening sensor in the data list with HDS after at least 1 minute under no load with no headlights, blower motor, rear defroster, radiator fan, A/C, etc. operating. Cars not equipped with a turbo charger For 2.62° or greater, Clean the throttle body. Turbo Charger equipped vehicle For 3.00° or greater, Clean the throttle body.",
